═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
RESILIENCE PATTERNS IMPLEMENTED
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

1. Retry with Exponential Backoff
   - Initial delay: 100ms
   - Backoff factor: 2x
   - Max retries: 3-5
   - Jitter: +-25% to prevent thundering herd

2. Circuit Breaker
   - Failure threshold: 5 consecutive failures
   - Open timeout: 30 seconds
   - Half-open: Allow 1 test request
   - Success threshold: 2 successes to close

3. Graceful Degradation
   - Return empty/default instead of 500 error
   - Log degradation for observability
   - Use stale cache when primary fails

4. Idempotency
   - SHA256 hash of payment details
   - Time-bucketed keys (per minute)
   - Prevents duplicate charges on retry

5. Timeout Protection
   - 5-second timeout on RPC calls
   - Deadline propagation via context

